OL,5, The father of a boy waiting for a heart
OL,6, transplant said he is devastated that  
OL,7, an opt-out organ donation system will  
OL,8, be delayed from taking effect due to   
OL,9, Stormont's stalemate.                  
OL,11,FMairtin MacGabhann told BBC News NI the
OL,12,Fdelay is unacceptable.                 
OL,14,FThe new law automatically makes people 
OL,15,Forgan donors unless they specifically  
OL,16,Fstate otherwise.                       
OL,18,FIt is named Daithi's Law, after        
OL,19,FMairtin's six-year-old son who is on   
OL,20,Fthe organ transplant waiting list.     
